&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dark Wolf&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;constructs and deploys data management and analytics solutions for the defense and intelligence communities. We’re proud to boast a world-class engineering team that thrives on rolling up their sleeves to solve your mission’s biggest challenges.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dark Wolf&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking a highly motivated and self-directed professional to fill the role of &lt;strong&gt;AI Lead Software Architect &lt;/strong&gt;to drive enterprise cloud data and AI initiatives. This role will focus on delivering scalable, secure, and high-performance platforms supporting advanced analytics and AI workloads. Architect and build enterprise-grade Agentic AI applications that combine LLMs, retrieval, structured data access, search,&amp;nbsp;orchestration, and workflow automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
