&lt;li&gt;Staying up-to-date on the latest Google Cloud services and technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementing security best practices for Google Cloud solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serving as the SME for all federal compliance requirements, including FedRAMP, NIST SP 800-53, and agency-specific security overlays&lt;/li&gt;
